profile:
At Cinehaus Theatre Concepts we believe in the right fit for each client. Our services range from a simple TV wall mounting and device setup to custom home theatre rooms with audio and video calibration. We'll take care of it all from possible reconstruction right through to the final calibration of your new system.

We like to make sure our clients are educated at the same time. You won’t just be left with a pile of remotes to figure out. That’s why we like to be involved in every step, making sure the components you get are best suited for what you want to do. Whether it’s a simple TV mounted on the wall with a soundbar, all the way to the big home theatre room with a 150” projector screen and a Dolby Atmos surround sound system. No job is too small, because everyone deserves a great entertainment experience at home!

We are centrally located in Kelowna, BC and we offer our services throughout the okanagan valley. Feel free to contact us and get yourself one step closer to a great entertainment experience.
